query:
UPDATE assessments a
SET 
  a.uniformatId = (SELECT bc.id FROM building_components bc WHERE bc.code = a.componentCode LIMIT 1),
  a.uniformatLevel = (SELECT bc.level FROM building_components bc WHERE bc.code = a.componentCode LIMIT 1),
  a.uniformatGroup = SUBSTRING(a.componentCode, 1, 1)
WHERE a.componentCode IS NOT NULL 
  AND a.componentCode != ''
  AND a.uniformatId IS NULL;
